OL,3,CStarmer set to announce 'game-changer'
OL,4,Csocial media restrictions for under-
OL,5,C16's
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer's demand that tech
OL,8,Ffirms stop children from taking and
OL,9,Faccessing nude images is not the end
OL,10,Fof his plans for them.
OL,12,FI've been told that he intends to
OL,13,Fannounce restrictions on social media
OL,14,Ffor under-16s ahead of the Makerfield
OL,15,Fby-election next week.
OL,17,FWhether this goes as far as an
OL,18,F"Australian-style ban" remains to be
OL,19,Fseen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
