PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781010670
OL,3,CStarmer set to announce 'game-changer'
OL,4,Csocial media restrictions for under-
OL,5,C16's
OL,7,FIt's thought that the PM may favour
OL,8,Fsomething a bit more nuanced than a
OL,9,Fstraight-up ban, perhaps with
OL,10,Fdifferent features limited to certain
OL,11,Fages.
OL,13,FSome social media platforms considered
OL,14,F"less harmful" may still be allowed
OL,15,Ffor children.
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
