FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781010670
OL,3,CStarmer set to announce 'game-changer'
OL,4,Csocial media restrictions for under-
OL,5,C16's
OL,7,FOne thing that is clear is that
OL,8,FStarmer's views on this have hardened
OL,9,Fover time.
OL,11,FThose who have heard him talk about
OL,12,Fthe issue say he often references his
OL,13,Fown children's positive experiences of
OL,14,Fsocial media.
OL,16,FBut it's also the case that the
OL,17,Fpublic, parliament and the Labour
OL,18,FParty all favour tougher restrictions
OL,19,Fand that Starmer may soon be looking
OL,20,Ffor the support of his own MPs in
OL,21,Fparticular.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781010670
OL,3,CStarmer set to announce 'game-changer'
OL,4,Csocial media restrictions for under-
OL,5,C16's
OL,7,FThe official line from Downing Street
OL,8,Fis that the government is "still
OL,9,Fconsidering" the responses to the
OL,10,Fconsultation on banning social media
OL,11,Ffor the under-16s.
OL,13,FBut a No 10 source adds that Monday's
OL,14,Fannouncement shows "the Prime Minister
OL,15,Fis forcing the tech companies to get
OL,16,Fon with it, he has stood up to Musk
OL,17,F(over the Grok AI tool) and we have
OL,18,Flegislated to act quickly once a
OL,19,Fdecision has been taken".
OL,26,@yD@ApmyD@Wpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
